Package files

Interface Summary
GenericFileStructure Interface for reading/writing delimited files
 

Class Summary
CompleteFileManager Extension of SimpeFileManager to read fields into a file.
FileParser Singleton for file parsing utilities
FileStructure Class to read and write from a delimited text file
MicroarrayFilter Microarray file format filter for JFileChooser
SimpleFileManager This Manager just converts a file to a LinkedList with the lines in the file of a list of strings to a file NOTE: This class is to be deprecated
TRNFilter TRN file format filter for JFileChooser
TRNParser A parser for different formats of TRN information to GML format Currently there's available: - SIF (Single Input File) format (STILL IN DEVELOPMENT) - SynTReN format Final GML format has the following keys: d0 - "node" - "name" - string - node name d1 - "node" - "type" - string - node type d2 - "edge" - "type" - ac|re|du - ac for activator, re for repressor and du for dual
